{"word":"H1100 - בְּלִיַּעַל - bᵉlîyaʻal - bel-e-yah'-al - Belial","slug":"H1100","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">בְּלִיַּעַל</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>bᵉlîyaʻal"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>bel-e-yah'-al"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Belial"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D1;&#x05BC;&#x05DC;&#x05D9;&#x05BC;&#x05E2;&#x05DC; - b<sup>e</sup>l&#x0131;&#x0302;ya&#x201B;al</b> - <i>bel-e-yah'-al</i><p/>From <a href=\"#/H1097\">H1097</a> and <a href=\"#/H3276\">H3276</a>; <i>without profit</i>, <i>worthlessness</i>; by extension <i>destruction</i>, <i>wickedness</i> (often in connection with <a href=\"#/H376\">H376</a>, <a href=\"#/H802\">H802</a>, <a href=\"#/H1121\">H1121</a>, etc.): - Belial, evil, naughty, ungodly (men), wicked."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1077\">H1077</a>, <a href=\"#/H1086\">H1086</a>, <a href=\"#/H1087\">H1087</a>, <a href=\"#/H1094\">H1094</a>, <a href=\"#/H1097\">H1097</a>, <a href=\"#/H1099\">H1099</a>, <a href=\"#/H1107\">H1107</a>, <a href=\"#/H1115\">H1115</a>, <a href=\"#/H8399\">H8399</a>"}]}